Actions.Text: REFERRED TO HOUSING, CONSTRUCTION AND COMMUNITY DEVELOPMENT

Title: Relates to transferring the village of Potsdam housing authority to the village of Canton housing authority; repealer
Summary: Transfers the village of Potsdam housing authority to the village of Canton housing authority; repeals provisions relating to the village of Potsdam housing authority.
LawCode: Rpld Art 13 Title 102, amd ยง520, Pub Hous L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public housing law, in relation to transferring the village of Potsdam housing authority to the village of Canton housing authority; and to repeal title 102 of article 13 of such law relating to the village of Potsdam housing authority
